# ── Cross-project reference clones (shared standard) ─────────────────────────
# Read-only clones of OTHER repos (e.g. the fairyfox.io hub), pulled on demand.
# Never commit them — see notes/reference/cross-project-sync.md.
assets/references/*
!assets/references/README.md

# ── Gradle / build output ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.gradle/
build/
.kotlin/
# The committed wrapper jar (gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar) stays tracked.

# Fabric Loom's working directories (client/fabric is a separate Gradle build).
# Loom caches a deobfuscated Minecraft and remapped dependencies here — large, machine
# specific, and fully regenerable.
client/fabric/.gradle/
client/fabric/build/
client/fabric/run/
client/fabric/*.log

# ── IDE / editor ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
out/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# ── OS cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Local scratch (build/test helper logs) ───────────────────────────────────
*.log

# Local test scratch (server smoke + mineflayer deps + local playtest server)
node_modules/
smoke-*/
run/
# NB: package.json + package-lock.json ARE committed now (the `npm ci` Mineflayer
# smoke needs the lockfile for Scorecard Pinned-Dependencies). Only node_modules is scratch.
